content: I bought this app for almost 8 dollar's with tax included, had high expectations because I love WMP in my PC but this version is very simple and not worth the money when you can find many more apps with a lot of features and audio enhancements . This Player has no EQ, no audio enhancements, etc, absolutely nothing. * Don't waste your time and money purchasing this app.
Want to like it, but can't figure out how to get to music stored on the SD card in my Moto Z3 and add it onto my "walking" playlist. Can't find additional info on this app anywhere. Help ....
